author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Oh, the first U-pa-ru-pa collab stream... Both are an amazing duet conceived as a team.
Rushia-daitenshi and Mahou Bunny Pekora-san were surprising in this stream.

Casually or not, in that time, both were a bit shy, but recently they've let go of their minds.

I hope Rushia-daitenshi and Mahou Bunny Pekora-san will make another Splatoon Stream or also a collab gameplay as team.
